# MAULER.md — project context file
#
# Place this file at the root of any project directory.
# TheMauler discovers it by walking up from CWD and uses it as a system
# prompt prefix for every request made while inside this directory.
#
# Rename to MAULER.md (remove .example) to activate.

# Context

This is a Go project targeting WSL2 on Windows 11.
Use `bash` tool commands that are Unix/bash compatible (not PowerShell).
Prefer standard library solutions before reaching for external packages.
When editing files, always read them first to understand the current state.

# Tools

# Uncomment to disable specific tools for this project:
# disable = ["web_search", "code_run"]

# Profile

# Uncomment to override the active model profile for this project:
# profile = "qwen3.6-think"

# Ignore

# Files/dirs to exclude from the file tree and context injection.
# Uses gitignore-style patterns (in addition to .maulerignore):
# vendor/
# *.pb.go
